# Session [4] – Network+

## Main Topics
- System haye adadi chist? (What is the system metrics numbers?)
- Binary, Decimal, Hexadecimal chetor kar mikonand? ( how does this work (Binary-decimal-Hexadecimal) ?)
- Faide ha va estefade ha dar networking ( the usege of this numbers in networking!)

## Flashback – Number Systems
- **Binary (Base 2)** = faghat 0 va 1
- **Decimal (Base 10)** = 0 ta 9, systeme shomaresh ma ensan ha
- **Hexadecimal (Base 16)** = 0 ta 9 va A ta F (10 ta 15)
- **Saurce ---> src فرستنده ( hich mac address dar donya eyksan nist )
-**Destination ---> dst گیرنده 

## Explanation
- Computer ha faghat binary mifahmand
- Networking baraye IP addresses, MAC addresses, mask ha az binary va hex estefade mikonad
- Tabdil decimal <-> binary <-> hexadecimal mohem ast
- Decimal 15 = Binary 1111 = Hex F
- Decimal 255 = Binary 11111111 = Hex FF
- Hexadecimal shortcut baraye binary ast (har hex = 4 bit)

